@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lisgfv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.73 / v2 + 0.61) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.07)))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.41)))
    tmp = (v2 + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.80) + tmp))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
